## Sign-Off

- **Free Beams (through launch week):** No formal sign-off. End with the Section 6 tease.
- **Paid Beams (post-launch):** Same. Beams are mid-week tactical pieces, not flagship Beacons. Reserve the formal "Keep the light on..." sign-off for Beacons and Horizon.

